## 4. Why Extension Instead of Playwright App

### 4.1 Playwright App Problem

Playwright is good for crawling, but bad for this case because ChatGPT login/session is protected.

Issues:

```txt
Cannot reliably login from automated browser
Headful manual login still may be detected
Cookies/session transfer is fragile
Automation footprint can trigger blocks
```

### 4.2 Extension Advantage

Chrome Extension runs inside the user’s real browser.

Advantages:

```txt
Uses existing authenticated session
No login automation
No cookie handling
Direct DOM access
Better UX
One-click export
```

Architecture shift:

```txt
From:
external crawler controls browser

To:
extension lives inside browser
```

This is the clean pivot.

