## 12. Markdown Output Contract

The generated `conversation.md` should follow:

```md
---
title: "{conversation title}"
source: "chatgpt"
sourceUrl: "{current url}"
exportedAt: "{ISO datetime}"
---

# {conversation title}

## User

...

## Assistant

...

![image](assets/001.png)
```

Role heading format:

```md
## User
```

```md
## Assistant
```

Do not add commentary.

Do not summarize.

Do not “clean up” the user’s original wording.

