## 13. Asset Handling

### Goal

Images should be local.

Bad:

```md
![](https://remote-cdn-url/image.png)
```

Good:

```md
![](assets/001.png)
```

### Asset Strategy

The extension should try these methods in order:

```txt
1. Read image src from DOM
2. Fetch image binary if CORS allows
3. Convert blob/data URL into file
4. If remote fetch fails, keep remote URL as fallback and mark warning
```

### Asset Naming

```txt
001.png
002.jpg
003.webp
```

Asset path:

```txt
assets/001.png
```

