## 19. Privacy and Security

This extension handles private user conversations.

Rules:

```txt
No external server
No telemetry
No analytics
No remote upload
No third-party API call
All processing local in browser
```

This is important because browser extensions can access sensitive page content, so the implementation should minimize permissions and avoid unnecessary data exposure.

Recommended permissions:

```txt
activeTab
scripting
downloads
host_permissions for ChatGPT only
```

Avoid broad permission:

```txt
<all_urls>
```

unless absolutely necessary.

